    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i'm always paranoid about it. but like, it's just a standard headache, not a major flare up or anything. i usually take 200mg of advil when i'm feeling off and it's fine. wouldn't a small dose like that just be totally fine for a one-time thing? i really need the pain to stop so i can sleep.",
