    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh my doctor is out of the office until monday and it's like 11pm here. i can't just wait three days with this headache, it's making me feel kind of nauseous too. isn't there like a safer alternative i can just grab from my cabinet? maybe something like tylenol? is that actually safe for my kidneys or is it the same thing?",
